1. CONFIRM the negative result: systematically verify that NO 8-element subset of F₇³\{0} at multiplicity 6 is short-zero-sum-free. Use the bitset DP (343-bit integers). If you find one, stop — that's a major discovery.

2. If no 8-element support works: search for longer zero-sum-free sequences.
   - Try 7-element supports at multiplicity 6 (length 42 < 49, always works by our theorem)
